00:26:25.440 --> 00:26:29.100
I had in hand Anne Foster's sworn
testimony, along with the account

00:26:29.100 --> 00:26:31.470
of that minister who
interviewed her in prison.

00:26:31.470 --> 00:26:34.050
But I also had to check
a number of details.

00:26:34.050 --> 00:26:39.050
For example, if in fact, you
