00:31:04.890 --> 00:31:07.820
that they didn't really do.

00:31:07.820 --> 00:31:13.320
But you know, there was this
situation in Central Park

00:31:13.320 --> 00:31:16.060
with the Central Park Five.

00:31:16.060 --> 00:31:20.750
These were teenage boys
and they confessed.

00:31:20.750 --> 00:31:24.110
The police worked them
over, but they confessed

00:31:24.110 --> 00:31:26.880
to crimes that they didn't commit.

00:31:26.880 --> 00:31:33.060
And I'm wondering what the process
is, whereby somebody's going

00:31:33.060 --> 00:31:35.740
to do something like that?

00:31:35.740 --> 00:31:37.930
&gt;&gt; Stacy Schiff: Turns
out to be remarkably easy

00:31:37.930 --> 00:31:39.510
to extract a false confession.

00:31:39.510 --> 00:31:43.220 position:56%
But it -- in the case of Salem, it's
exacerbated by a few other issues.

00:31:43.220 --> 00:31:47.570
First of all, with some of the
