00:31:47.570 --> 00:31:49.230
they are actually tortured.

00:31:49.230 --> 00:31:51.770
And we have evidence of the
fact that they had been hung

00:31:51.770 --> 00:31:56.030 position:56%
up in a rather grotesque fashion, to
have the truth extracted from them.

00:31:56.030 --> 00:32:00.590
But many of the people who
are brought in are women.

00:32:00.590 --> 00:32:02.250
Many of them have never been --

00:32:02.250 --> 00:32:04.500
have never stood before
an authority before.

00:32:04.500 --> 00:32:08.560
The men who were interrogating them
