but I don't know if I couldn't

00:33:00.550 --> 00:33:04.340
because I was innocent, or if
the Devil was stopping my words."

00:33:04.340 --> 00:33:05.640
So there's a certain confusion.

00:33:05.640 --> 00:33:08.690
Everyone feels he has a
spot on his conscious;

00:33:08.690 --> 00:33:11.280
a blemish on his conscious
of some kind.

00:33:11.280 --> 00:33:13.980
And there's -- because there's no
such thing as a guilty conscious

00:33:13.980 --> 00:33:18.170
in the 17th Century, that must
feel diabolical in some way.

00:33:18.170 --> 00:33:20.720
By mid-summer, the
confessions begin to run rampant

00:33:20.720 --> 00:33:22.850
for an additional reason.

00:33:22.850 --> 00:33:25.450
Which is that it had
become clear to people

00:33:25.450 --> 00:33:28.110
that if you confessed,
you did not hang.

00:33:28.110 --> 00:33:31.430
So only the people who resist the
authorities who go to the gallows.

00:33:31.430 --> 00:33:35.020
And so confession is used as an
additional means of protection.

00:33:35.020 --> 00:33:37.650
And of course inside every
confession is a gleaming bit

00:33:37.650 --> 00:33:39.540
of shrapnel known as an accusation.

00:33:39.540 --> 00:33:41.080
Because if you confess,
you generally hand

00:33:41.080 --> 00:33:43.140 position:56%
